wiki.content:
Sometimes love can seem like an unfinished symphony.You start out knowing who you  need to love, some people are lucky enough to find that person and hold on to them for the rest of their lives. Very sadly, for various reasons other relationships come to an end.... There again  end sounds  permanent, but is not always the case. It is possible to reach out and find the one and only once again..........Destiny plays its role.  Not Goodbye, just Au Revoir for  now..................Voilá that symphony can and will be finished!!
